{"tid":1859911,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"奉俊昊《上流寄生族 Parasite》全新黑白版本 電影中心限定上映","createTime":"2020-02-03T11:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T09:01:28.000Z","uid":4260,"like":42,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d9e84534ca35bb6879c14d6aae9c607cf6c6bb5e","tid":1859911,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:41:20.000Z","msg":"《上流寄生族》 推出全新黑白版本電影 ‼️‼️<br />\n百老匯電影中心都有得睇 (&bull;&oline;⌣&oline;&bull;)<br />\n<br />\n點解《上流寄生族》 出黑白版？原來都是因為導演奉俊昊 的「虛榮心」～他曾說過：「當我想到經典電影時，它們全部都是黑白的。因此我認為，如果把我的電影變成黑白，那麼它們就會成為經典。」亦透露出早在去年參加康城影展前，他就已經做好黑白的版本喇～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/83524659_2637726389608294_1323515793127768064_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQlFghUbSkMTgqPxjGNipE_Np2cwdXl0u2Wzis2nUkKFOzLBWFW_8Cr5DGGtv6cLFgE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=f6883028e2bb146fc15a7978680257e8&amp;oe=5ED68C8E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F83524659_2637726389608294_1323515793127768064_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQlFghUbSkMTgqPxjGNipE_Np2cwdXl0u2Wzis2nUkKFOzLBWFW_8Cr5DGGtv6cLFgE%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Df6883028e2bb146fc15a7978680257e8%26oe%3D5ED68C8E&h=4a57520a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5bfb12e70c4f03e8149061bf1943708384897a6","tid":1859911,"uid":157092,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家唔敢入戲院"},{"pid":"233fd873d275da3d166b8126d0afe4da4154cc34","tid":1859911,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:46:51.000Z","msg":"Nice"},{"pid":"2a3dcf165ec0c84006f9161de1b8e0eb2e0f28b5","tid":1859911,"uid":4260,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGzRx8T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGzRx8T.jpg&h=2fc865c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼早前係鹿特丹電影節首映之後，將在紐約同洛杉磯既戲院限定上映<br />\n<a href=\"https://deadline.com/2020/01/neon-release-date-black-and-white-parasite-bong-joon-ho-1202838397/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fneon-release-date-black-and-white-parasite-bong-joon-ho-1202838397%2F&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=1dc90427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://deadline.com/2020/01/neon-release-date-black-and-white-parasite-bong-joon-ho-1202838397/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pmcdeadline2.files.wordpress.com/2020/01/image002-1-e1579735568909.jpg?w=681&amp;h=383&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpmcdeadline2.files.wordpress.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fimage002-1-e1579735568909.jpg%3Fw%3D681%26h%3D383%26crop%3D1&h=757a3696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pmcdeadline2.files.wordpress.com/2020/01/image001.jpg?w=1024&amp;h=549\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpmcdeadline2.files.wordpress.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fimage001.jpg%3Fw%3D1024%26h%3D549&h=ddea832c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"935094e39d5c1371a60906078428fadffbc470b1","tid":1859911,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5bfb12e70c4f03e8149061bf1943708384897a6","tid":1859911,"uid":157092,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家唔敢入戲院"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T12:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05762f2992862a90dea4c459c77a95c9dd06fe7","tid":1859911,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a5bfb12e70c4f03e8149061bf1943708384897a6","tid":1859911,"uid":157092,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:43:43.000Z","msg":"